<br>
This is quite a change to EQ. It's changing one of the core operations of the game. So it's going to take some time i'm sure. I hope noone will start jumping to conclusions and saying how this sucks and things of that nature until we finally see how it all pans out. </font><P><b><i><font size=3><font color=blue>Molex Evilslayer<BR>
55 Knight<BR></b></i></font>
